        {
            "title": "全球AI大咖飛印度參加峰會！卻少了黃仁勳",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"全球AI大咖飛印度參加峰會！卻少了黃仁勳\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"639\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/0Z.jFh0I1SxzpRQ9jZsubQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOQ--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/c9514630-0af8-11f1-9f9f-57320bbd7e6f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">全球AI大咖飛印度參加峰會！卻少了黃仁勳</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83ai%E5%A4%A7%E5%92%96%E9%A3%9B%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%8F%83%E5%8A%A0%E5%B3%B0%E6%9C%83-%E5%8D%BB%E5%B0%91%E4%BA%86%E9%BB%83%E4%BB%81%E5%8B%B3-033004035.html",
